Class GrouperVersion_v3414

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mmm.cms.homehealth.AbstractGrouper
      • com.mmm.cms.homehealth.AbstractGrouper_2

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HomeHealthEventNotifierIF, HomeHealthGrouperIF, Describable, Initializable, Namable, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GrouperVersion_v3514

    public class GrouperVersion_v3414
extends AbstractGrouper_2
implements HomeHealthGrouperIF
    This version is valid from January 1, 2014 to September 30, 2014. There is not grace period and no start window. In previous versions, the OASIS-C record was mapped back to the OASIS-B record after validation but prior to scoring. This version removes this mapping and scores directly on the OASIS-C record.
    Author:
    3M Health Information Systems for CMS Home Health
    See Also:
